{"tid":1961814,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"依日Last Day...","createTime":"2020-04-07T05:01:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T11:07:48.000Z","uid":94771,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"c82dbdb124fc10cf962b4de9605a07646413a160","tid":1961814,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:01:21.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">屌你,係啊Last Day啊。英國查警暴 同 廢佬優先排隊諮詢ＬａｓｔＤａｙ啊<br />\n</span></div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VnQi2Ut.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVnQi2Ut.jpg&h=8efc9595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n急！英國下議院收集濫暴警察高官名單，麻煩各位於4月7日前於以下網頁提交黑警違反人權之證明，不要讓手足白白犠牲。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkinquiry.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkinquiry.org&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=94d86220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkinquiry.org</a><br />\n詳情： <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/109945333953726/posts/121574426124150/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F109945333953726%2Fposts%2F121574426124150%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=7a907cfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/109945333953726/posts/121574426124150/</a><br />\n📣 請訂閱作戰研究院 Telegram Channel ➼ @FightResearch<br />\n戰術研究 | 抗爭資訊 | 時局分析 | 評論 | 趣事<br />\n<br />\n反對修訂70歲以上人士優先投票及限制公眾監票人數<br />\n<br />\n唔好同我講有咩用，Send個Email唔係好難為你G，做佐先<br />\n唔好咁撚懶得唔得<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mFchy3u.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmFchy3u.png&h=42e709f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HaUS7ou.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHaUS7ou.png&h=21678823&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTemplate，自己轉下Ｄ字同標題，唔係人地會轉去垃圾電郵唔計數<br />\n<br />\nfor懶人 反對修訂70歲以上人士優先投票及限制公眾監票人數<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1918375\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1918375</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主就寄佐信<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YiLSnXS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYiLSnXS.png&h=21203a71&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後希望大家幫手打Twitter戰妓同Reddit戰線<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JrguqbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJrguqbQ.jpg&h=3db59f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AYucnYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAYucnYw.jpg&h=c582c27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0GffkLb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0GffkLb.jpg&h=c2f75a5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國際文宣組:<a href=\"https://t.me/internationalfuckccp54321\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Finternationalfuckccp54321&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=5512bd66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/internationalfuckccp54321</a><br />\n新手Twitter任務:<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=c73dd673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\nReddit戰線:<a href=\"https://t.me/redditmansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fredditmansyunzou&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2lezv6TERBNTdTd%2BiGQaA%2FLRg%3D&h=3f6bccae\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/redditmansyunzou</a>"},{"pid":"348c5550451994633e929bf2181d3dafec69b44a","tid":1961814,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:01:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"54e257e8f165b5ec3bca755829dec69b04cff541","tid":1961814,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:01:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c6903961bca67473572ad517bbde82600164fe9","tid":1961814,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:01:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"584e04782a306286e822486bebd1acba6fc3ae4a","tid":1961814,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:02:12.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">和理非要練習做【哨兵】</span></div></span></div><br />\n<br />\n見到狗車就影一影，之後報上Telegram台<br />\n你可能救返好多手足<br />\n好多人味做過，唔敢踏出第一步，但行出第一步，你會發現唔係咁難做。<br />\n哨兵變成習慣係最理想，狗會無所遁形，手足被埋伏的風險大大降低，拎起手機偷偷影偷偷報哨<br />\n反正香港人偷影咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔明對你地有咩難度<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ptFhQQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FptFhQQi.jpg&h=0c8e7731&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建議返屋企同Ｄ 【黃】屋企人裝Telegram <br />\n教埋佢地報哨<br />\n唔好睇少師奶請報網，佢地唔洗返工，又成日要周圍買菜<br />\n好有用<br />\n佢地有時做起野上來，熱心個我地<br />\n50人做，50隻眼，1萬人做，1萬隻眼<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/up5NtBS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fup5NtBS.png&h=20c094d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>狗仔圖鑑</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zLiLfhP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzLiLfhP.jpg&h=4d1c8caa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jwREjKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjwREjKu.jpg&h=c53e7c1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOAmx4v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOAmx4v.jpg&h=08b86bab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JuB5fhQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJuB5fhQ.jpg&h=46403cc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c76deba06be5e95e8562050f7f2f90f9becf6a5a","tid":1961814,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:02:53.000Z","msg":"二十三條立法，只係快慢問題<br />\n9月之前，9月之後。<br />\n遲定早都 特區政府都一定會立<br />\n<br />\n依家對面就係製做輿論，創做一個有利二十三條立法的空間出來<br />\n<br />\n可以點？文宣戰不能未打先輸<br />\n一於去買一疊A4 size label周圍貼! 文宣都可以遍地開花, 等政府同藍絲都清唔晒!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">低風險 低門檻 低成本<br />\n唔使再因為冇膽玩噴膠 怕俾人報串而做唔到文宣</span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TH2tr0q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTH2tr0q.jpg&h=86093f0b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>一般文具舖都有! 預100蚊100張</ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gGj9UyA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgGj9UyA.jpg&h=0b180dc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你鐘意寫字又得，拎去做底印文宣都得<br />\n<br />\n二十三條文宣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sZjaDY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsZjaDY3.jpg&h=e1b8bae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XzMXiY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXzMXiY3.jpg&h=55b77da7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ek1XiY4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEk1XiY4.jpg&h=c6eb8ba3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YGoR7Sp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYGoR7Sp.jpg&h=0ba9f508&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QFWHu5L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQFWHu5L.jpg&h=dc4e878f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3YgcSi6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3YgcSi6.jpg&h=78abcdde&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家潮流興貼交通工具<img